{"tid":2091384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"皇軍譴責四個傳媒協會反映不專業行為","createTime":"2020-07-02T16:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T17:11:40.000Z","uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa67995b666872a8c596b289304a920dc613b711","tid":2091384,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"【警方致函四個傳媒協會反映不專業行為】<br />\n<br />\n昨日(7月1日)，銅鑼灣及灣仔一帶有暴徒破壞社區設施、縱火堵路，<del>警方</del>皇軍到場執法時，發現有人竟假冒記者，亦有個別網上媒體報道時有欠專業。<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午，<del>警方</del>皇軍在百德新街近怡和街的示威現場中，發現一名穿著黃色並寫上「PRESS記者」背心的女子，她當時沒有進行採訪工作。傳媒聯絡隊上前了解後，發現她並非記者。而她之後涉嫌非法集結被捕。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有警員在高士威道近興發街制服一名涉嫌參與非法集結的疑犯期間，被多名<del>暴徒</del>示威者包圍襲擊，身體被利器插傷，大量出血。有網媒竟然美化搶犯、襲擊警務人員的惡行，將事件報道為「防暴按倒示威者 市民合力擊退落單警」。該網媒顛倒是非的報道，令人不齒。<br />\n<br />\n至傍晚，時代廣場有人將大量印有警員個人資料的單張撒在地上，有網媒竟以特寫鏡頭，近距離拍攝及直播警員的資料，有關做法極不專業，亦可能違反有關禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n<del>警方</del>皇軍對於有人假冒記者及個別媒體表現有欠專業感到遺憾，已於今日發信予香港記者協會、 香港新聞行政人員協會、 香港新聞工作者聯會及香港攝影記者協會表達關注及反映事件。"},{"pid":"c62a1257d0ffaafd1fe996390d8ca0244d00e505","tid":2091384,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/photos/pcb.3308557585898849/3308559859231955/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.3308557585898849%2F3308559859231955%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=dbc29d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/photos/pcb.3308557585898849/3308559859231955/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"977912ef1fb8998374e41de447c72a43c5577a62","tid":2091384,"uid":302784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"做法不理想，已經作出內部訓示"},{"pid":"786834d1d85dfcfd951e23b00b54c7d4e25ee3ce","tid":2091384,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"做法唔理想 已訓斥"},{"pid":"aa402d688d07b5d9b794c1f80e24c13c305f6b33","tid":2091384,"uid":2284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"而家記者要冒好大風險 仲慘過戰地記者 遲d 記者都唔敢上"},{"pid":"20feec00253814c38a3fce4bddf6d70de454950b","tid":2091384,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"當年皇軍應該專業d<br />\n殺哂全部支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48c9b8a2f28f4c7e8eae41e295834c3d9db154d","tid":2091384,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔專業方面，警察的確係權威"},{"pid":"3fe31226c8b20bc1b37c7569b72a81aa888cf7d1","tid":2091384,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"傳媒聯絡隊上前了解後，發現她並非記者。<br />\n咩叫並非記者？基本法寫左有新聞自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d9eb1ad30528889b8eb9a4fba429ff3b9a6642","tid":2091384,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"發現一名穿著黃色並寫上「PRESS記者」背心的女子，她當時沒有進行採訪工作。傳媒聯絡隊上前了解後，發現她並非記者。<br />\n<br />\n咩叫並非記者？依家香港做記者要攞牌？<br />\n皇軍又借啲意為審查記者鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed51e2f390d3ce1c6d569f67a2f881954d83edc2","tid":2091384,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"唔理想"},{"pid":"9b3fcc4bfd18224ba89afd8a94570fb0f67b489f","tid":2091384,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"假冒記者係記協問題?? 傻鳩唔係扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多年黎有人冒警 即係狗隊都係垃圾不專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef66c69c6cfb2c17e98cd6e783569d903f2d1c7","tid":2091384,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"3 6 7 9，0 2 4 2！<br />\n<br />\n3 9 2 2，0 1 7 6！<br />\n0 2 2 0，3 9 2 2！<br />\n7 9 0，8 8！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3467ac9bc779e645c5d1299d591510feace42f1e","tid":2091384,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"水炮車射記者呢"},{"pid":"b9104bc0a862465bf19990691c6e0deff1100546","tid":2091384,"uid":273289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"佢唔係記者姐係唔關記協事啦。。。。。"}]}